a:17:{s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";s:11:"small_descr";s:107:"Diabecon is an ayurvedic blend of over 30 herbs and minerals and provides gentle and safe glycemic control.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:143:"Diabecon ist eine ayurvedische Mischung, die aus 30 Kräuter und Mineralen besteht. Es wirkt, um eine leise und sichere glykämische Kontrolle.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:124:"Diabecon est un mélange ayurvédique de plus de 30 herbes et de minéraux qui assure le contrôle glycémique doux et sûr.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:123:"Diabecon es una combinación ayurvédica de más de 30 hierbas y minerales que provee un control glucémico suave y seguro.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:117:"Diabecon è una miscela ayurvedica di più di 30 erbe a minerali che procura un controllo glicemico salvo e delicato.";s:10:"full_descr";s:1225:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Diabecon promotes glucose utilization and helps maintain normal blood sugar levels. It helps maintain healthy triglycerides and cholesterol levels.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>Take 2 tablets twice daily, 30 minutes before meals on an empty stomach. Not intended as a substitute for blood sugar level testing or professional medical care. If needed, may increase to 2 tablets three times daily. Natural products treat not just the symptoms but the body as a whole and take time for absorption and results.</p><p>If you miss a dose of this medicine and you are using it regularly, take it as soon as possible. Do not take 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>2 tablets twice daily, 30 minutes before meals on an empty stomach. If needed, may increase to 2 tablets three times daily.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>There are no warnings or precautions for Diabecon usage.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>Diabecon tablets are not known to have any side effects if taken as per the prescribed dosage.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:7:"36.2976";s:9:"pack_name";s:7:"bottles";s:4:"type";s:4:"caps";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:60;a:10:{i:5184;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5184";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"60.496";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5185;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5185";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"47.05244";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5186;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5186";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"42.57126";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5187;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5187";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"40.33067";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5188;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5188";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"38.98631";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5189;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5189";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"38.09007";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5190;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5190";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"37.4499";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5191;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5191";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"36.96978";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5192;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5192";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"36.59635";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}i:5193;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5193";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"36.2976";s:4:"name";s:8:"Diabecon";}}}}